# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values.

```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

---

# Required

# PostgreSQL connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/finance_dashboard

# JWT signing secret — use a long random string (min 8 chars)
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-in-production

# ---

# Optional (defaults shown)

# Token expiry — accepts any value valid for jsonwebtoken (e.g. 1h, 7d, 24h)
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=24h

# Port the server listens on
PORT=3000

# Environment — affects logging and error detail exposure
NODE_ENV=development
